# Climate Action Hackathon Malaysia 2025
### *Urban Heat & Flood Resilience  (SDG 13: Climate Action)*

This project is a responsive, accessibility-friendly event website created for Climate Action Hackathon Malaysia 2025, focusing on SDG 13: Climate Action with emphasis on urban heat and flood resilience.
It provides event information, schedules, speakers, tracks, datasets, registration, and sponsor details.

### Features
- Fully Responsive Layout
Works on mobile, tablet, and desktop using CSS Grid & Flexbox.
- Clean UI & Consistent Styling
Uses custom CSS variables for colors, spacing, radius, and shadows.
Minimalistic and modern design.

-Accessibility Optimized
Includes skip to content link.
Semantic HTML tags (header, main, section, nav, ul, figure, etc.).Focus states on interactive elements.

- Structured Event Sections
Hero banner
Event details
SDG 13 explanation
Timeline schedule
Speakers & mentors
Tracks & challenges
Malaysian open-data resources
Registration form
Sponsors
Contact & FAQ
Footer credits

### Technologies Used
Technology	Purpose
HTML5	Structure and content of the website
CSS3	Layout, grid, animations, styling
Responsive Design	Mobile-first layout
ARIA attributes	Better accessibility
